00:04:11.300 --> 00:04:13.680
given by Heisenberg's
Uncertainty Relation,

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:16.034
they can make the two
photons identical.

00:04:19.180 --> 00:04:22.985
And when, let's say, experiment.

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:34.470
Well, you have two NV
centers, defects in diamond.

00:04:34.470 --> 00:04:39.190
You can manipulate with
microwaves coherently the spin.

00:04:39.190 --> 00:04:43.670
You need lasers for
initialization and readout.

00:04:43.670 --> 00:04:46.330
But then closer to what
we want to discuss,

00:04:46.330 --> 00:04:50.370
