with the double well,

00:27:36.788 --> 00:27:41.072
isn't there going to be-- all
right, some people would say

00:27:41.072 --> 00:27:44.447
you spontaneously break the
symmetry and [INAUDIBLE]

00:27:44.447 --> 00:27:48.848
either ends up in one
