00:28:21.300 --> 00:28:23.020
Well, that's their
job, so to speak.

00:28:23.020 --> 00:28:24.370
That's their job description.

00:28:24.370 --> 00:28:26.540
And if you have a
minuscule difference

00:28:26.540 --> 00:28:30.590
between the two, the
